        <abstract>
            <p>Has found Verlot.</p>
            <p>His sister [Emily Catherine Langton] is dying [d. 2 Feb 1866].</p>
            <p>His stomach still very bad. Writes one or two hours and reads a little.</p>
            <p>JDH is a wretch to remind CD of his coal-plant prophecy.</p>
            <p>Glad JDH will give Nottingham lecture.</p>
        </abstract>
